      • operate

        void operate(Population parents,
           Population offspring)
        Performs the genetic operator. Crossover should take the parents in pair from the parents population, clone them, perform the operation and put the offspring into the offspring population.
        Parameters:
        parents - the population of parents
        offspring - the population of offspring
